<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/xeicon@2.3.3/xeicon.min.css"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@300;400;500&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css" />
    <title>Home → Best Horror Scenes → An ever growing collection...</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="left">
        <div class="inner">
          <h1 class="title"><a href="/"> BEST HORROR SCENES</a></h1>
          <div class="intro">
            <p>
              An ever growing collection featuring some of the best scenes in
              horror.
            </p>
            <p>
              “Best Horror Scenes” is a collection of scenes I feel are some of
              the most affecting in horror. Some may be simple black cat scares,
              others may be more subdued or nuanced. Many come from films that
              aren't necessarily “horror” but have elements or threads of
              horror.
            </p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="">Newsletter</a>
              <a href="">Suggest a Scene</a>
              <a href="">YouTube</a>
              <a href="">Twitter</a>
              <a href="">Contact</a>
              <a href="">RSS</a>
              <a href="">Letterboxd</a>
            </div>
            <p>
              Best Horror Scenes is a love letter to the Horror film genre by
              Brandon Durham. Most film clips contain major spoilers, and it is
              recommended you don’t watch the clip if you plan on seeing the
              film.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="right">
        <!-- 상단 고정창 start -->
        <nav class="top_fixed">
          Currently viewing <span class="filter_btn" id="filter"><%= nationEn %></span>
          sorted by <span class="sort_btn" id="sort">random</span>.
        </nav>

        <!-- filter menu -->
        <div id="filterMenu" class="filter_menu">
          <div class="s_head">
            <h4>FILTER BY</h4>
            <i class="xi-close xi-2x"></i>
          </div>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <span class="category" data-nation="">everything</span><span class="cnt">0</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="category" data-nation="대한민국">Korea</span
              ><span class="cnt">0</span>
            </li>
            <li><span class="category" data-nation="미국">USA</span><span class="cnt">0</span></li>
            <li><span class="category" data-nation="영국">UK</span><span class="cnt">0</span></li>
            <li>
              <span class="category" data-nation="일본">Japan</span><span class="cnt">0</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="category" data-nation="중국">China</span><span class="cnt">0</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- sort menu -->
        <div id="sortMenu" class="sort_menu">
          <h4>SORT BY</h4>
          <i class="xi-close xi-2x"></i>
          <ul>
            <li class="category">random</li>
            <li class="category">release year</li>
            <li class="category">title</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- 상단 고정창 end -->
        <!-- 본문 start -->
        <div class="movie_info">
          <%for(let i = 0; i < list.length; i++){%>
          <article>
            <div class="tit">
              <h2 class="movieName" id="movieName">
                <%= list[i].title %> <%= list[i].repRlsDate %>
              </h2>
              <span
                >Directed by&nbsp;<span class="director" id="director"
                  ><%= list[i].director %></span
                ></span
              >
            </div>

            <div class="main_txt">
              <div class="video_box">
                <div class="tag" id="tag"><%= i +1 %></div>
                <img src="<%= list[i].poster %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="main_txt_wrap">
                <p><%= list[i].plot %></p>
                <span class="keywords"><%= list[i].keywords %></span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cmt">
              <span class="view">No comments</span>
              <span class="write"
                ><i class="xi-speech"></i>&nbsp;<span>Leave a Comment</span
                >&nbsp;</span
              >
            </div>
          </article>
          <div class="gradient"></div>
          <%}%>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <div class="youtube"></div>
      <div class="twitter"></div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
<script src="/js/script.js"></script>
